description: Oscar Properties Holding AB engages in the acquisition, development, and marketing of real properties. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm and currently employs 23 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2013-06-18. The Group buys, develops and sells real estate properties in central Stockholm with focus on both new properties as well as on converting older buildings, such as schools, factories or post offices for residential use. Oscar Properties Holding AB's portfolio of completed projects amounts to approximately 500 apartments. In August 2014, it acquired all shares of Oscar Properties Gasklockor AB.
